OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FConservationists have mapped out more
OL,7,Fthan 70,000 weirs, dams and other
OL,8,Friver barriers across the UK, warning
OL,9,Fthat they are a "huge problem" for
OL,10,Fwildlife and pollution.
OL,12,FA new database compiled by
OL,13,Fenvironmental charity WildFish reveals
OL,14,Fthere is an average of one manmade
OL,15,Fbarrier for every 2.5km (1.5 miles) of
OL,16,Fwaterway across 150,000km (93,000
OL,17,Fmiles) of rivers across Britain.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
