FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FMany of these weirs, concrete dams,
OL,7,Funderwater gates and other barriers
OL,8,Fare "old, redundant" installations
OL,9,Fthat serve no practical purpose, the
OL,10,Fcharity says.
OL,12,FWildFish warns that these structures
OL,13,Fmake it difficult for fish and other
OL,14,Fwildlife to migrate, create areas of
OL,15,Fconcentrated pollution and affect the
OL,16,Foverall health of the habitat.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FThese manmade obstacles are eight
OL,7,Ftimes more prevalent than natural
OL,8,Fbarriers such as waterfalls, which
OL,9,Fonly occur around once every 20km (12
OL,10,Fmiles) on average, WildFish said.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, data on barriers in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland is scarce, with fewer
OL,14,Fthan 100 obstacles recorded on the
OL,15,Fcountry's thousands of kilometres of
OL,16,Frivers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
