FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FBarriers can damage the entire river
OL,7,Fecosystem, with 674 rivers in England
OL,8,Ffailing to achieve good ecological
OL,9,Fstatus in 2023 due to blocks to fish
OL,10,Fmigration, the charity said.
OL,12,FRiver blockages are a driving factor
OL,13,Fin declines for four of the seven
OL,14,FBritish freshwater species that are at
OL,15,Frisk of extinction - Atlantic salmon,
OL,16,FEuropean eel, allis shad and twaite
OL,17,Fshad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FBut not all hope is lost, WildFish
OL,7,Fsuggests, as when barriers are
OL,8,Fremoved, rivers can quickly restore
OL,9,Ftheir flow and fish return.
OL,11,FThe charity is calling for the
OL,12,Fgovernment action on removing barriers
OL,13,Fwhere possible to help restore rivers
OL,14,Fand wildlife.
OL,16,FWildFish data analyst Daniel Nixon
OL,17,Fsaid: "River barriers have long been a
OL,18,Fhuge problem for wildlife, pollution,
OL,19,Fand river health, yet the issue has
OL,20,Freceived little attention ` perhaps
OL,21,Fdue to a lack of comprehensive data.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,F"WildFish's database now reveals the
OL,7,Ftrue scale of the problem, with more
OL,8,Fthan 70,000 barriers mapped across the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,F"While the number of barriers is
OL,12,Foverwhelming, there is also real hope:
OL,13,Fwhen unnecessary barriers are removed,
OL,14,Frivers typically respond quickly, with
OL,15,Friver flow restoring and fish
OL,16,Freturning to previously inaccessible
OL,17,Freaches."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
