FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FThe charity said the biggest hurdle to
OL,7,Fremoving weirs, culverts or other
OL,8,Fbarriers is planning and legal
OL,9,Fpermissions which can take months or
OL,10,Fyears to secure, with go-ahead
OL,11,Frequired from organisations such as
OL,12,Fthe Environment Agency, councils or
OL,13,Finternal drainage boards.
OL,15,FWhere removals do go ahead, however,
OL,16,Fthe barrier can be gone in a matter of
OL,17,Fhours, often just for the cost of
OL,18,Fhiring a digger or jackhammer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
