FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FWildFish hopes the database ` which it
OL,7,Fsays is the most complete inventory
OL,8,Fyet of the barriers across UK rivers `
OL,9,Fwill raise awareness of the issue and
OL,10,Fhelp identify redundant barriers to
OL,11,Fimprove river health.
OL,13,FA typical example on the map is a weir
OL,14,F` a small dam to regulate river flow `
OL,15,Fat the end of Ennerdale, in the Lake
OL,16,FDistrict, which maintained water
OL,17,Flevels when the lake was used as a
OL,18,Freservoir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
