FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt is now a redundant structure that
OL,12,Fblocks fish such as the migration of
OL,13,FAtlantic salmon, who make migrations
OL,14,Fof more than 1,000 miles, as well as
OL,15,Fsea trout, brook lamprey and European
OL,16,Feels, the charity said.
OL,18,FAn Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,19,Fsaid it "recognises the scale of the
OL,20,Ftask to tackle barriers to fish and
OL,21,Feel migration".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
