PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779718269
OL,3,CMore than 70,000 barriers in UK's
OL,4,Cwaterways putting wildlife in danger
OL,6,F"Working as part of the Great
OL,7,FYorkshire Rivers Partnership we have
OL,8,Fremoved over 100 barriers so far," a
OL,9,Fspokesperson said.
OL,11,F"We know there is more to do to
OL,12,Fimprove river connectivity across our
OL,13,Fwaterways and as part of our
OL,14,Fpartnership work we aim to remove
OL,15,Fthousands of barriers across the
OL,16,Fcountry within the next two decades."
